  "title": "5 days Civil Engineer up to $5000",
  "description": "<p>Civil Engineer</p><p>Salary: $3,800 – $5,000<br />Working Hours: 8am - 5pm (Mon to Fri)<br />Work Location: Pulau Bukom / Jurong Island / Assigned project sites<br />Benefits: 14 days Annual Leave, Bonus</p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Plan and manage daily site construction or maintenance activities</li><li>Coordinate subcontractors, suppliers, and internal teams</li><li>Monitor site progress and resolve technical or site issues</li><li>Prepare work schedules, reports, and site documentation</li><li>Assist with method statements, risk assessments, and inspections</li><li>Support procurement activities, progress claims, and cost control</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety, quality, and HSSE requirements</li><li>Participate in site meetings and project handover activities</li><li>Support defect rectification during the Defects Liability Period (DLP)</li></ul><p></p><p>Job Requirements</p><ul><li>Degree in Civil Engineering (Singapore PE Board–recognized preferred)</li><li>Minimum 3–5 years of relevant site experience</li><li>Familiar with construction planning and documentation</li><li>Proficient in MS Project or Primavera (preferred)</li><li>Strong coordination, communication, and problem-solving skills</li><li>Able to work independently and on site as required</li></ul><p><br /><br /><br />Company Name: Talent Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 24C2338</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Loke Sai Lye (Loke)</p><p>EA Personnel No: R24123366</p><p>Email: loke.dexter@talentrecruitmentsg.com</p><p>Contact Number: 8168 8648</p>",
